  <h2>Research</h2>
  <p>
    In order to understand and analyze the ways SoundCloud was used, I conducted
    interviews over Zoom and Discord with target demographics to discover key
    information I was looking for.
    <br />Details of the interviews were as follows:
    <ul>
      Interviewee criteria - Those who have previous experience in using
      SoundCloud's mobile app<br /><br />

       Research objectives:
      <li>To uncover primary usage of the app</li>
      <li>To learn about types of activities conducted on the app</li>
      <li>
        Finding design opportunities based on activities conducted leading up to
        the usage of the app
      </li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <img
    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dbiwj2oo8/image/upload/v1642579525/Frame_4_hf5lfm.png"
  />
  <!-- <img
