  /> -->
  <p>
    <small>A summary of key insights from interviews.</small>
  </p>
  <p>
    Through this process, I learned that a primary use case amongst my
    interviewees included listening to <strong>instrumental soundtracks</strong>
     while they conducted their day-to-day tasks such as studying or doing their
    chores. Their issue with this was that while they open SoundCloud when they
    intend to be productive, they may
    <strong
      >unintentionally leave the app when they get distracted from their task.</strong
    >, at which point the music stops playing. This lead to my problem
    statement:
  </p>
  <p>
    <h2 class="sansserif">
      How might we minimize the chances of users unintentionally stopping their
      music?
    </h2>
  </p>
